"{\"uid\": \"dailypost.ng-2024-02-28-2024-olympic-qualifier-super-falcons-vs-banyana-showdown-gets-dates-venues\", \"text\": \"Published  on  By  The Super Falcons of Nigeria will host the Banyana Banyana of South Africa in the first leg of the 2024 Olympic Games final round qualifier on, Friday, April 1, 2024.  The encounter will hold at the Moshood Abiola Stadium, Abuja.  The reverse fixture will take place at the Mbombela Stadium, Mpumalanga eight days later.  The overall winners will seal a place at the Paris 2024 Games.  The Super Eagles are looking to make a return to the Olympics after a 16-year absence.  South Africa on the other hand have failed to qualify for the last two editions of the games.  Paris, France will host the 2024 Olympics between July 26 and August 11, 2024.  Ngannou had good outing against Fury, I am ready to fight - Anthony Joshua  Guardiola hails Alonso amid Liverpool managerial speculation  2024 Olympic Qualifier: Banyana boss anticipates tough contest against Super Falcons  2024 Olympic Qualifier: Waldrum unveils squad for Super Falcons vs South Africa  2024 Olympic Qualifier: It's do or die vs Super Falcons - South Africa coach, Ellis  2024 Olympic Qualifier: South Africa set up final round clash with Super Falcons  2024 Olympic Qualifier: Why I benched Oshoala against Cameroon  2024 Olympic Qualifier: South Africa boss Ellis sets sight on Super Falcons clash  Copyright \\u00a9Daily Post Media Ltd\"}"